Historic Data For Mississippi River at E: Located at the entrance to Empire Lock at river mile 29.5.

Gage reset to NAVD88 (2004.65) on 29Nov2005. All prior historic stage data is relative to NGVD29.  To adjust the historic data (from 24Feb1987 to 29Nov2005 only) to NAVD88 (2004.65), subtract 0.79 feet.
Gage reset to NAVD88 (2009.55) on 01Jul2015. To adjust NAVD88 (2004.65) data to NAVD88 (2009.55), subtract 0.6 feet.
Gage data from 26Sep18 to present diverged, so subtract 0.12 feet to adjust to NAVD88 (2009.55).
To adjust NAVD88 (2009.55) values to 2007 Low Water Reference Plane (LWRP) datum relative to NAVD88, subtract 0.2 ft.
